- Schutta is a cloud-focused architect at Thoughtworks.
- He coauthored Presentation Patterns, wrote Thinking Architecturally and Responsible Microservices, and teaches at the University of Minnesota.
- He’s also a seasoned speaker who regularly presents at worldwide conferences.
- Dan Vega, a Spring developer advocate at Broadcom and a Java Champion, has over 20 years of software development experience.

